# Web (Next.js) Rules
- App Router + Server Components by default; Client Components only when needed.
- Tailwind for styling; use design tokens/components, no ad-hoc inline styles.
- All user-facing strings go through i18n (EN/IT/ES) — no hardcoded copy.
- Fetch data through the typed API client; never call the DB directly.
- Keep components small and accessible (labels, roles, keyboard support).
